document_data.mainbody:
'''''The Complete Spacefarer's Handbook''''' is a 2{{nd}}-edition ''Advanced Dungeons & Dragons'' accessory. It is part of the ''Spelljammer'' campaign setting.

{{quote|
''Out of the depths of [[wildspace]] come astonishing new ideas for SPELLJAMMER campaigns. Now you can create player characters from the nonhuman races of the [[giff]], [[dracon]]s, [[scro]], [[grommam]]s, and more. Equip your characters with kits like the Corsair, War Mage, and Aperusa. Then add some new space-oriented proficiencies and equipment, enlist your character in a spacefaring organization, and head off into the Void!''
}}

document_data.Dedication:
The book was dedicated to [[Curtis Scott]], and contained a memorial message on the credits page.
{{quote|
''Respectfully dedicated to the memory of Curtis Scott, lost tragically in an auto accident August 19, 1992. He will be missed by the many friends he touched through his writing and gaming.''}}
